Titolo: Parkasaurus

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Parkasaurus is a dinosaur zoo construction and management simulation video game developed by Washbear Studio. It has entered Steam Early Access on September 25, 2018, with the official release being on August 13, 2020. The player is tasked to create a dinosaur zoo by building and designing dinosaur exhibits. On December 15, 2021, it was announced in an Indie World Direct that the game was being ported to the Switch in Spring of 2022.

Genere: Construction and management simulation

Valutazione: 70
